  "title": "instantsearch.js - v2 roadmap to release",
  "body": "High level issue centralizing the progress of the implementation of instantsearch.js v2.\r\n\r\nConnector:\r\n- [x] Remove clearAll position from connector @bobylito \r\n- [x] TemplateProps hierarchicalMenu\r\n- [x] Discuss the  tility of checking the rendering function\r\n- [x] Expose connectors @iam4x\r\n- [x] Make the widget pass all the options to the rendering as a black box @iam4x \r\n- [x] Ensure \"items\" connectors consistency (currentRefinement, refine, items[{isRefined, value, name}]) @iam4x\r\n- [x] Nested template options and transform data, remove? / items clear currentRefinedValues\r\n- [x] Make sure every widget rendering gets the instantseach instance @bobylito\r\n- [x] Remove `container` / `DOM` references into connectors tests @iam4x\r\n- [x] Remove the need of `attributeNameKey` in connectHierarchicalMenu @iam4x\r\n\r\nV2:\r\n - [x] JSDoc of connectors/widgets\r\n - [x] Generate doc website\r\n - [x] drop react completly for oustide users @iam4x\r\n - [x] Change the default sort order (like #1529 but keeping the ability to override) @iam4x\r\n\r\nRelated issues:\r\n - Connectors #1923 \r\n\r\nDogfooding connectors (tested custom components): \r\n - [x] connectMenu",
